<div id="outline-container-org4dc4a01" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org4dc4a01"><span class="section-number-3">5.3</span> Frostbite</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-5-3">
<p>
When a chracter takes damage from the cold and the temp is 0 or less
and their extremities are not properly covered, they might develop frostbite.
Damage is dealt first to these extremities but still counts toward your total hitpoints.
A point of damage to your ear is still a point of damage to you.
</p>
<table border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" rules="groups" frame="hsides">


<colgroup>
<col  class="org-left" />

<col  class="org-right" />

<col  class="org-left" />
</colgroup>
<thead>
<tr>
<th scope="col" class="org-left">Body Parts Exposed</th>
<th scope="col" class="org-right">Damage Distribution</th>
<th scope="col" class="org-left">Damage until Frostbitten</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="org-left">Just Feet</td>
<td class="org-right">all</td>
<td class="org-left">4 pts.</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">Just Ears</td>
<td class="org-right">all</td>
<td class="org-left">6 pts</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">Just Hands</td>
<td class="org-right">all</td>
<td class="org-left">8 pts</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">Hand &amp; Ears</td>
<td class="org-right">1:1</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">Feet &amp; Ears</td>
<td class="org-right">2:1</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">Hands &amp; Feet</td>
<td class="org-right">1:1</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
</tr>

